Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard stories, but I never
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,imagined it would be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This place holds secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She only needed one interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago Quint was the billionaire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,no one could reach, and that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,story could save her career.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So she accepted the most
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,dangerous deal of her life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to be his girlfriend for one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to be simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk into the ball convinces
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,family and walk out with the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,answers she
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,needed, but when
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago's mother demanded proof of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,love in front of everyone, she
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,did exactly what she
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She kissed Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that kiss, which was only
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,supposed to be a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,started to feel far too real.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Impossible Interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,His room smelled of reheated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:00:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee and old paper, and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.86,0:01:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina Pike had already drunk
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,cups before nine in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The gray light coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the window gave every face there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the same shade of exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of fatigue that doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,come from one bad night's sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but from months piled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,one on top of another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.62,0:01:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew, hers was no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She held her folder against her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,chest, and crossed the narrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,aisle between the desks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,greeting with a Kurt Nord anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who looked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis Vaughn was waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,her with his elbows planted on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the desk, glasses pushed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to the tip of his nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The editor had a peculiar way of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at people, as if he were
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,checking whether they were
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,worth their own salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina shut the door behind her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ignored the chair he didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,offer, and sat down without
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the interview Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis didn't waste time on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,introductions, and I need
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,something else too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're about to tell me you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,need a photo of Quint without
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,his jacket, I'm walking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,out of this room right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a file.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The sentence landed in the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,middle of the desk, like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,something too heavy for the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:01:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina raised an eyebrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for him to refraise to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,apologise to turn it into a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis did none of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He simply laced his fingers, and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,kept looking at her, as if he
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,were collecting on an old
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Proof, he added, that that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,empire is hiding something it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't be hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone hides something Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to find out what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to get inside the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,home of the most closed off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,family in the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Land the interview no one's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,managed to land in 10 years, and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,still walk out of there with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,compromising material.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that your job
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,here depends on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat staring at the coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,stain on the rim of his mug.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Calculating how much of next
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,month's salary was already
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,committed to rent, how much was
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,still owed on her mother's bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The window behind Hollis let in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the muffled noise of the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A horn, a quick step.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The city running nonstop while
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,she sat there deciding how far
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,she was willing to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she nodded once, short,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone signing a contract
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,they haven't yet read.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Malo Trent intercepted her in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the hallway with two fresh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,coffees, and a smile that was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,already a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Malo was a copy editor, a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,colleague of three years, and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the only person in the newsroom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,who understood when Rowine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,needed silence, and when she
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,needed noise, you look like
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,someone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,who just sold her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Malo remarked, handing over the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,hotter cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it for much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was for next month's rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Malo laughed, a short laugh, cut
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,off halfway by the awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that the joke was worth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,more to herself than to Rowine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She leaned her shoulder against
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine as they walked down the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway, and for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine felt like dropping
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,everything right there, walking
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,out the front door and never
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She drank the coffee until it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,burned her tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,After noon came quickly, and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with it a note left at the front
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No sender, just her name on the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,front of the envelope, written
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in black pen and handwriting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that wasn't a friend, slanted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,controlled letters, each one in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:03:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,its exact place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine had turned the envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,over twice before opening it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,inside just an address and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The office it pointed to was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,three blocks away, in a discreet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,building she had never noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,despite having walked past it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,hundreds of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The sign at the entrance simply
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,read Ashford and Associates, in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,letters too small to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,draw attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine aclimed the steps with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,her folder still pressed against
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,her chest, and greeted
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the receptionist with the name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that was on the note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who received her was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,younger than she expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tall, navy, suit, no tie, with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that kind of discretion only old
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,money teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He extended his hand and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,introduced himself as Silas
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashford, the Quint family's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a friend of Jago's since their
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,boarding school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The information came without
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,fanfare, the way someone hands
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,over a business card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat, Miss Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice had the same tone as
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the handwriting on the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be brief because the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,proposal is brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Quint agrees to grant a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,two-hour interview to your
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,publication.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No restrictions on subject
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Except one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas made a minimal pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of pause lawyers used
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to let the client swallow the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,next piece of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In return, you would attend the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,family's Gallaboll in Savannah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as his companion on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One night, just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine elapsed before her brain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,authorized her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the word he preferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And what word didn't he prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The corner of Silas's mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,moved half a millimeter, almost
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of a smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but nothing followed through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He slid a black envelope across
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the desk, sealed, with her name
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,written on the front,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same slanted, controlled
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,handwriting as the first note.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Letters she now recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,without effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and which definitely did not
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,belong to Silas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules are in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One read is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The expects an answer today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine looked at the black
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought about the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought about the look on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Holasis face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought about the old
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,photograph of the reclusive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,billionaire
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that had circulated through the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,papers forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Always the same profile of a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,clenched jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Always the same gaze that didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,invite anyone to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She tucked the envelope into her
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,folder without opening it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him I'll be in Savannah on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas nodded like someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,already knew the answer before
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He rose, shook her hand again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and walked her to the door with
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,practice courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Before closing the handle, he
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,said almost without voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not what the press writes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine didn't ask what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She preferred not to know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Marla was waiting for her on the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,street with a cigarette that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,pretended to be lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of theatre she used as
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,an excuse to loiter on corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine handed over the black
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope without ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend turned the object over
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in her hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,studied the seal with more
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,attention than necessary, and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,gave it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't open it now, Marla said,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,open it on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's prettier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be someone else's
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,story or make history?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's the second, you open it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,on the train alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and you cry if you need to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,without anyone seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the least you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine laughed and the laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled some of the weight off
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She rested her forehead on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Marla's shoulder for a short
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just enough to remember she
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,still had a friend in that grey
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,city,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and then she went home to pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The station was too crowded for
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,her taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine had dragged her luggage
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,between hurried bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,bought a sandwich she wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,going to eat, and settled by the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,window of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The seats smelled of dust and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,warm synthetic leather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That smell of a place where many
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,people have passed without
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat staring at the tracks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,before taking the black envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the inner pocket of her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The seal gave way with a dry
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside, three folded sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The first two carried
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,instructions written with almost
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,legal precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Times, names she should
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,memorize,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,clothes that would be delivered
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What to say if anyone asked how
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,long they had known each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine erred them with the same
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,attention she gave to story
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,contracts,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,mentally noting every detail,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,every gap between the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The third sheet was smaller, a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,single line written by hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,unsigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't smile at anyone like you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Only smile when I'm looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She read it three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She put it away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked out the window as the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,train picked up speed and the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,city opened into suburb,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,then countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And she couldn't decide whether
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that was an order, a warning, or
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The train arrived in Savannah in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the late afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The air changed before she even
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,stepped onto the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Warmer, denser,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,laden with a sweet perfume she
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't yet name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnolia maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something that grew near
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine across the station with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,her folder under her arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for the driver who would
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,be waiting with her name on a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She found the dark car outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a man in a suit opening the back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,door without ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Before getting in, she looked
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,one last time at the city's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,skyline and saw in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The high roof of the quint
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion cut against the sky that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,was beginning to turn orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Too big, too old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of house that doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,invite you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It absorbs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine sat on the leather seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,rested her head against the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and pressed the black envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,against her lap,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone clutching a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,boarding pass to another
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She took the sheet out one more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Only smile when I'm looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She re-read it, folded it, put
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The car started up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the streets of Savannah
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,began to pass by outside like a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,borrowed set,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with the moss heavy trees and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the old houses that each guarded
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,their own version of a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the first time since
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Holly's Vaughn had added the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,word file,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine a pike wondered,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,whether she could go home as the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,same person who had boarded the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 2, a three second kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who tell sweet was bigger than
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,her entire apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,with a soft smell of jasmine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that seemed built into the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:09:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine looked at herself in the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,oval mirror for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,adjusting the wine-colored silk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,dress they had left hanging
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,behind the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The fabric fell effortlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of piece that only
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,existed when someone paid for it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,without thinking twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The driver knocked at the door
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,at the exact time indicated in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine went down,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,crossed the lobby under stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,she pretended not to notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and found the car waiting at the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,curb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The back door opened before she
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,touched the handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the first thing she saw
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,inside was the impeccable crease
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of dark trousers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,running down to a pair of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,polished black shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago Quint was seated on the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,other side of the seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with one knee slightly apart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,from the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,hands resting on his own thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't stand, didn't extend
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He merely tilted his chin and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,inch toward the empty spot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,beside him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine got in, adjusted her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,skirt with a quick gesture,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and shut the door with more
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,force than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw that he noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of them commented.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Miss Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice was lower than she had
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,imagined from any interview
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd ever read.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A voice that didn't rise because
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it didn't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine returned her face and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at him full on for the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and had the displeasure of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,confirming that the portraits
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,published over the years did
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,him no justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In person, he was a sculpture of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a straight jaw,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,dark hair combed back with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,calculated carelessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and eyes that decided the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,temperature of the room before
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,saying anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Mr. Quint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Rowine will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He nodded almost imperceptibly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the car started up, and for a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,while the two of them sat in
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine noticed his hands resting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,on his knees,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,long fingers, a silver watch
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with no visible brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She also noticed that the seat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,between them held a thin leather
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,folder,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,closed, with one corner leaning
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,against the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She collected details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the rules clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked without turning his
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:11:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine awaited until he finally
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,turned his gaze to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you intend for this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,night to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as necessary, that's not
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only one I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked forward again and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine accepted defeat in that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,round without arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept watching his profile
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,against the dark window.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The hard line of his jaw, the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,way his thumb pressed against
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,his own knee in a steady rhythm,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone counting something
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,inside himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She stored the gesture in her
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,memory, and said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Quint mentioned appeared at
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of the avenue of tall
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,lit from outside like a theatre
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,set.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine drew a deep breath before
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the car stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago got out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Went around the vehicle and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,opened her door with a courtesy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that sounded more rehearsed than
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He offered his arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,His palm brushed briefly against
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,her hand as he helped her
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,position herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and the temperature changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't smile at anyone like you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,believe it, he murmured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Barely moving his lips as they
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,climb the steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You already warned me in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:12:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reinforcing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The main hall swallowed them the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,moment the door opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine has smelled it before she
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,saw anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnolia and old money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly as Silas had said in the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,instruction note.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The white walls rose high to a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ceiling of worked stucco,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and everywhere there were
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,antique chandeliers spreading a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,honey-colored light over the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Long dresses, emerald chocas,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,men in black tuxedoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,greeting each other without
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago introduced her to three
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,couples in a row,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,always with the same assembled
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My companion for the evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine a pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No complicated surnames.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine a smile in just the right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Answered questions in just the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,right measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And noticed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She noticed that he avoided the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,terrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice a waiter passed offering
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to take guests out to the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,outdoor area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And both times Jago declined,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with a minimal gesture of his
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,chin,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,without even looking at the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,glass door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She also noticed that his gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,had one point,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,tripped over an empty chair near
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A chair upholstered in dark
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,green velvet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,slightly set apart from the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of the arrangement,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,as if it belonged to someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,used to sit there and hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked away quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowineerstorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unlikely evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The voice came from behind her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,sweetest syrup heated too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine returned and found a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,woman with red hair pinned in a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,low bun,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,an emerald green dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,a smile that didn't reach her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago stiffened beside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Odeit, he greeted her without
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Odeitmachand extended her hand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to Rowine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,palm down,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the gesture of someone expecting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,reverence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I write.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Odeit seemed to decide something
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How brave of him to bring you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Brave of me to agree to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Odeit laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A short note that contained
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing of laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she moved off with a wave
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of her fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving behind a trail of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,expensive perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago rested his hand at the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,small of Rowine's back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for just a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a gesture of ownership that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he withdrew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't need to provoke her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He remarked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Low.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I did, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But the corner of his mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,moved a millimeter,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rowine arrested it as if it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,were the headline of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a smile yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence in the hall changed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,texture
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,before she understood why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if the air had drawn
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,back a few inches,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody there in Unison
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,had turned their heads in the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,same direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowine followed the others gaze,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and saw you door a quint
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,entering through the main door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The matriarch didn't need to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,announce herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A long black dress, a pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,necklace that fell to the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of her chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,gray hair pinned with a rigidity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that allowed no discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She crossed the hall without
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,greeting anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and stopped before her son and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,his companion,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,with the expression of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,appraising merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, mother, said Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You'dora didn't answer her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She turned her pale eyes to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and examined her from shoes to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,hairstyle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with a surgical calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she stepped half a step
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and the voice that came out of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,her was low,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but sharp enough to cut the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,entire hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see love here, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence closed around the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina felt Jago's body
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,stiffened beside her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,his shoulders rising half an
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora stayed put, chin raised
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Proof said the matriarch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's true, prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire hall turned, heads
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,lifted from champagne glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,conversations ceased,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,waiters stopped where they
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,stood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina felt the weight of the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,whole hall falling on her and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw that he locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,His thumb stopped counting on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,his own hip,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,his jaw hardened,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and for a whole second, no
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,decision came out of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina decided for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She raised her hand took his
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,face by the side and pulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His mouth met hers with a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,hesitation of someone who hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,rehearsed this scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and for an instant, Rowina
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,thought he wouldn't respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then his breath faltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She felt the falter,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,felt the air caught halfway up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,his chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,felt his hand rise by reflex to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,her back and settle between her
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder blades,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with a pressure that didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,belong to the charade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The kiss was supposed to last a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It lasted three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina lost count somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,between the moment he tilted his
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,head a little to the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and the moment she herself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,forgot there was a hall around
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When they pulled apart, she
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,opened her eyes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He took half a second longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and what Rowina saw on his face
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when he finally looked back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,was the same thing she felt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and which she wasn't prepared to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Udora stepped back half a step.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She adjusted her pearl necklace
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with a calculated carelessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and the corner of her mouth drew
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,a line that wasn't a smile but
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,pretended to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mermaid the matriarch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to see you again many
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Many.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She turned on her heels and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,moved off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The hall little by little began
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to breathe again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Conversations returned like a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,discreet murmur.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Waters moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone laughed in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,at something that wasn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina kept looking at Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand was still on her back
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in no hurry to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He took his time pulling it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When he did, his fingers passed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly over the silk of the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone memorizing a path
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,they might need to retrace
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Across the hall Odec-Marshon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,watched them with a glass in her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and her smile was now a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,different one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina registered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She already knew, without
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,needing a warning,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that that woman would want
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago leaned in very slightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and spoke close to her ear so
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,low that only she could hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For the kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For the length of the kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't know the answer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She took the glass away to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,drank a sip she didn't even feel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:18:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,go down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and looked again at the empty
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,chair near the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, at some point, had sat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who now was no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rowina Pike, who had
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,collected details since
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,understood that the most
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,important story of that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,had nothing to do with the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,reason Hollis Vaughan had sent
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 3, Coffee with No
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning after the ball
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived without ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the Savannah Sun came through
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the gaps in the curtain of the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,guest room,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Quint Mansion with an
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,almost impolite insistence,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rowina Pike opened her eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,before she remembered exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,where she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It took a whole instant for the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,high ceiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the carved footboard, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,thick silence of the house to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,organize themselves in her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Only then did the kiss come
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It came back first through her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,lip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then through the nape of her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then through her stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Three seconds that now carried
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the weight of biography.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat on the edge of the bed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and looked at her own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They were cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone had left a coffee tray
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,on the sideboard beside the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,door,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,during the night probably,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because the cup was no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,steaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Beside it a short note, written
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,by hand in a hand writing she
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,garden, whenever you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jay Rowina re-read the note
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,twice just to prove to herself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that it hadn't unsettled her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The garden was at the back of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the house, far from the main
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She noticed that as a small
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,paleide housekeeper,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,let her down a corridor of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,portraits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman introduced herself as
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,neve,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,lightly squeezed Rowina's arm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in an accent from rural Georgia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that Mr. Jego was already
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There was warmth in her voice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but also scrutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina smiled with her mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,closed and asked nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jego Quint was standing near an
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,old rose bush with his back to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,White shirt sleeves folded to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the elbow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,hair still wet from his shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He turned when he heard the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,gravel and for a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,just one, his eyes met hers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,unguarded,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,without their usual controlled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,gleam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then his jaw firmed up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I could, she
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,answered,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the house makes noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It does. He pointed with his
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,chin toward a cast iron bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to work out what comes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina obeyed, but chose to sit
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in profile knees turned outward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A small defense he noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the interview, Jego
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,began,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,his voice low and chosen word by
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's still standing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but last night raised an issue I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't foresee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother didn't believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,until the kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she believed it afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you disappear tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll get suspicious again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll have three candidates
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,on the table by Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me for more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina swallowed the small shock
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and breathed through her mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,before answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Weeks of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A dinner here and event there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough for Savannah to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the woman who finally got
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:21:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,into this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.14,0:21:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He paused.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Same payment, same interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a longer timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There was logic in the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew both.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I refuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you get the interview anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He said without hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed on something and I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,don't undo what's agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what disarmed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The resolution of the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina bit the inside of her
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Looked at the nearest rose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,counted to three and said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He just nodded slightly, like
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,someone closing her claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But when she stood up to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,into the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,his hand brushed her back for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,half a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,had a spot below her shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And lingered an instant longer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,than any contract required.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.64,0:22:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She stored the gesture alongside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She was already collecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The following weeks arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and without a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina began to split herself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,between the newsroom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.48,0:22:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where Marlo covered her shifts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with increasingly irritated
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,humour,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the streets of Savannah,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,where she learned there were
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:22:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,neighborhoods where the air
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:22:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,smelled of wet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.82,0:23:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jasmine and others where it only
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,smelled of hoarded money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.50,0:23:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jego always sent for her at the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,station,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,with the same driver and always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He waited for her inside, in the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,back seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.26,0:23:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder leaning against the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,opposite door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One Tuesday, he took her to an
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,antique's fair under the oaks of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the old
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina stopped in front of a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,tray of loose pendants,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.80,0:23:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and picked up one shaped like a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,crooked owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Half green with age, set with
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ridiculous red stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ugly, she said, smiling at
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the object as if it were an
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, Jego agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She put the pendant back on the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.77,0:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't haggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't look at it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.22,0:23:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Half an hour later, when they
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,were heading back to the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,he passed the dark velvet box
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.87,0:23:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,into her hand without any
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.56,0:23:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rowina stood in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of the sidewalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,holding the crooked owl as if it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,were a live animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.80,0:23:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't haggle, she remarked.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he opened the car door for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew what it was worth to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:23:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It was that day that Rowina
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't turn on the recorder for
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.91,0:24:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.46,0:24:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat with Jego in his office
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,on the 13th floor of a glass
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,building in downtown savanna,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and they talked about things no
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.19,0:24:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,interview called for.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.54,0:24:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A cousin he had never saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.58,0:24:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A book she had read 12 times in
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.24,0:24:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,her teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.78,0:24:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A specific smell of the coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,her mother used to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.20,0:24:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Jego poured her coffee that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.69,0:24:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon in a way she hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,taught him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.12,0:24:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Half a spoon of sugar, a splash
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.81,0:24:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.74,0:24:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Very hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina looked at the cup, looked
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.88,0:24:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,at him, and didn't ask how he
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.62,0:24:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.32,0:24:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Neeve let the answer slip a week
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.10,0:24:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,later in the mansions kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.28,0:24:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,while drying a crystal glass
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.64,0:24:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,with the attention of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.05,0:24:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,handling something bigger than a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.61,0:24:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.38,0:24:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been sleeping better since
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.62,0:24:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you've been coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.92,0:24:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The housekeeper didn't look at
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.36,0:24:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina as she said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.42,0:24:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a compliment, it's an
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.33,0:24:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.00,0:24:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina laughed softly without
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.68,0:24:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,breath to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.10,0:24:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know something
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.57,0:24:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.22,0:24:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Neeve continued, putting the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.73,0:24:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,glass away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.76,0:24:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.11,0:24:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone asked him how his day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.50,0:24:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,was.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.06,0:25:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He would be grateful, even if he
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.75,0:25:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't know how to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.60,0:25:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina's hand trembled slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.06,0:25:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,on the handle of her mug.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.58,0:25:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She set the mug down on the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.87,0:25:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,marble with doubled care.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.52,0:25:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The charity event took place on
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.89,0:25:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.38,0:25:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an auction in aid of a
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.13,0:25:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,children's hospital in a vaulted
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.06,0:25:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,ceiling tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.14,0:25:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,where the candleabras seemed too
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.77,0:25:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,heavy for the wire that held
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.20,0:25:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.90,0:25:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina wore a dark green dress
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.28,0:25:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,borrowed from Marlo's sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.06,0:25:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and Jago appeared at her side at
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.67,0:25:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the entrance, as if he'd matched
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.27,0:25:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the exact time to his own watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.42,0:25:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Odec Marshaar arrived 20 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.37,0:25:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,later.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.18,0:25:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina saw her approach from the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.49,0:25:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,other side of the hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.76,0:25:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,greeting people with thin
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.95,0:25:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,kisses.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.82,0:25:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A champagne coloured dress
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.24,0:25:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,moving like liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.28,0:25:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Odec stopped in front of Rowina,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.20,0:25:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,looked her up and down with a
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.94,0:25:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,smile too polite to be polite,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.22,0:25:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and said in a tone that carried
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.64,0:25:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,through the three nearest
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.78,0:25:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,people,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.56,0:25:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you hold up well dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.96,0:25:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A borrowed dress in a hall of
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.39,0:25:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,this caliber isn't for just
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.72,0:25:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.46,0:25:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the night is kind to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The air in the hall became
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.76,0:25:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.70,0:25:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Two women near the buffet
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.91,0:25:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped chewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.34,0:25:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina felt the blood rise up
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.94,0:26:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,her neck and choose between
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.44,0:26:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,turning into fury
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.38,0:26:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and turning into dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.00,0:26:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Before she could decide, Jago's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.08,0:26:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,hand touched the small of her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.02,0:26:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.78,0:26:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Firm, without theatrical
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.38,0:26:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,possession, just presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.70,0:26:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and he took half a step forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.38,0:26:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder pressed against hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.30,0:26:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Odec, he said, and his voice was
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.38,0:26:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer lower than usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.72,0:26:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,only stripped of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.84,0:26:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,amiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.62,0:26:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any doubts about the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.21,0:26:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,woman I came with, put those
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.61,0:26:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,doubts to me directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.32,0:26:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina owes you no explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.83,0:26:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,about where she buys any dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.74,0:26:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.40,0:26:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Odec parted her lips, and
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.05,0:26:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,something inside her smile gave
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.10,0:26:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,way for half a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.02,0:26:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,before recomposing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.46,0:26:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now touchy Jago, it was a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.67,0:26:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.66,0:26:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.66,0:26:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't raise his tone, he
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.22,0:26:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.34,0:26:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people nearby rediscovered a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.01,0:26:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,sudden fascination with their
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.52,0:26:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,own shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.56,0:26:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Odec nodded, murmured a phrase
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.33,0:26:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,about finding a friend and with
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.16,0:26:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.86,0:26:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago didn't move his hand from
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.34,0:26:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina's back for a few more
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.72,0:26:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.58,0:26:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and in those seconds she felt
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.91,0:26:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.42,0:27:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,His thumb resting exactly on the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.57,0:27:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,seam of her dress, the heat of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.58,0:27:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,his palm,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.64,0:27:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the silent weight of being
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.04,0:27:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,chosen there before an entire
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.61,0:27:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.28,0:27:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When he moved his hand away, it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.77,0:27:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,was slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.82,0:27:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina drew a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.22,0:27:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.60,0:27:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I did, actually, he answered,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.37,0:27:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,without looking at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.02,0:27:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew what she was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.90,0:27:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the night passed in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.37,0:27:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.18,0:27:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina won a small lot with the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.83,0:27:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,money she had, a pair of glass
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.43,0:27:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,earrings no-one wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.26,0:27:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago won nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.30,0:27:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He just watched her from afar,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.23,0:27:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,from across the hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.00,0:27:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and every time she raised her
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.51,0:27:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes, he was already looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.52,0:27:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They returned to the mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.77,0:27:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,around midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.00,0:27:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She went up to the guest room
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.35,0:27:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and stood for a long time in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.66,0:27:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,front of the open suitcase on
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.01,0:27:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.90,0:27:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,at the bottom of it, under two
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.89,0:27:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,folded blouses, and a pair of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.82,0:27:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,old shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.02,0:27:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.22,0:27:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown, no label, tied with a
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.38,0:27:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,rubber band.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.72,0:27:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina pulled it into her lap,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.34,0:27:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,sat on the rug and stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.69,0:27:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.48,0:27:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.54,0:27:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She ran her thumb along the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.19,0:27:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,edge, drew a deep breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.00,0:28:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and returned the file to the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.14,0:28:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,bottom of the suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.70,0:28:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She folded the blouses over it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.34,0:28:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with exaggerated care, as if
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.88,0:28:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,covering it were enough to undo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.58,0:28:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what labour-neath.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.90,0:28:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A phone on the nightstand
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.19,0:28:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,vibrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.28,0:28:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina glanced sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.24,0:28:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A missed call.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.52,0:28:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then another.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.34,0:28:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a third one she watched
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.57,0:28:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.40,0:28:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pollis Vaughan's name blinking
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.84,0:28:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,on the screen like a silent
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.13,0:28:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.76,0:28:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She let it ring until it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.90,0:28:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.72,0:28:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept looking at the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.03,0:28:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,until the light went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.16,0:28:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When she lowered her head again,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.23,0:28:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the phone vibrated a fourth
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.98,0:28:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.84,0:28:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.00,0:28:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina closed her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.60,0:28:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Across the corridor, someone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.27,0:28:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,walked slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.70,0:28:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear feet on the wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.36,0:28:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew who steps they were,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.88,0:28:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and she didn't open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.76,0:28:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone kept.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.90,0:28:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 4 The File She Wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.61,0:28:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.34,0:28:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.08,0:28:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pollis Vaughan's fifth call came
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.87,0:28:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,just after dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.20,0:28:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time, Rowina answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.56,0:28:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She was sitting on the floor of
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.76,0:28:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the guest room,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.34,0:28:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,still in the wrinkled green
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.06,0:28:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.78,0:28:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The glass earrings in her lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.56,0:28:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone trembling in her hand
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.22,0:29:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sixth time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.70,0:29:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The rug beneath her smelled of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.11,0:29:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,old lavender.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.38,0:29:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of lavender that isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.87,0:29:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.88,0:29:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.06,0:29:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You vanished, said Hollis
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.30,0:29:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,without a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.82,0:29:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice had that measured calm
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.64,0:29:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that preceded fireings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.26,0:29:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard your voice in
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.39,0:29:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.38,0:29:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.12,0:29:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.44,0:29:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.82,0:29:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is the material.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.40,0:29:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.32,0:29:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.78,0:29:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.32,0:29:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina closed her eyes and
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.53,0:29:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,rested her forehead on her knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.44,0:29:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The knee was cold through the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.86,0:29:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,wrinkled fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.12,0:29:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside the garden hadn't quite
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.73,0:29:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,woken up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.76,0:29:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A shallow grey light spread
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.21,0:29:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,across the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.64,0:29:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the day was still
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.71,0:29:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,convincing itself to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.54,0:29:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pollis.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.52,0:29:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.40,0:29:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He drew a deep breath on the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.44,0:29:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,other end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.76,0:29:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I backed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.92,0:29:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.16,0:29:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Paid for the hotel the first
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.48,0:29:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,weekend, kept your shift going
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.89,0:29:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with Marlo covering three
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.06,0:29:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,straight shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.20,0:29:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a benefactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.46,0:29:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.02,0:29:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And an editor needs to deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.58,0:29:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Either you send me something by
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.85,0:29:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday night or I'll have to
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.00,0:29:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,make a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.62,0:29:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,neither of us once.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.10,0:30:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.88,0:30:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside, a bird insisted on the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.73,0:30:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,same short note near the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.22,0:30:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rowina caught herself
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.40,0:30:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking about how Jago used to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.87,0:30:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,be late with the coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.56,0:30:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever there was a bird
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.59,0:30:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.42,0:30:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd stand out on the porch for
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.71,0:30:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.56,0:30:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,listening, the cup forgotten in
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.34,0:30:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.28,0:30:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She shouldn't have noticed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.04,0:30:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She had noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.40,0:30:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.48,0:30:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She said finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.20,0:30:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.64,0:30:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.76,0:30:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.90,0:30:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday night, headline or
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.28,0:30:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.68,0:30:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He hung up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.06,0:30:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina kept looking at the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.45,0:30:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,for a length of time she
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.48,0:30:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.64,0:30:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The reflection of her own
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.95,0:30:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,distorted face on the black
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.35,0:30:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.18,0:30:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She stood up slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.74,0:30:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She walked to the suitcase which
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.21,0:30:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,was half open on a wooden chair
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.64,0:30:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,near the dresser.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.58,0:30:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She pulled the brown file out by
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.31,0:30:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the rubber band, sat down again
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.99,0:30:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,on the rug,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.98,0:30:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and rested the file on her own
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.49,0:30:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.38,0:30:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands were still this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.84,0:30:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stiller than she expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.04,0:30:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She untied the rubber band
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.49,0:30:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.46,0:30:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She opened the first flap.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.26,0:30:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Clippings of balance sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.30,0:31:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Photocopies Hollis had obtained
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.81,0:31:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,from some discrete source.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.46,0:31:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Notes in small handwriting
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.95,0:31:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,written by herself before she
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.60,0:31:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,met Jago Quint.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.00,0:31:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In a gray, noisy newsroom where
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.67,0:31:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the coffee was bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.06,0:31:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and ambition still seemed enough
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.50,0:31:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to pay the bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.82,0:31:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina read two lines of her own
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.40,0:31:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,field notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.58,0:31:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and didn't recognize the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.96,0:31:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who had written that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.12,0:31:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She closed the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.10,0:31:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She tied the rubber band again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.46,0:31:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She put everything back at the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.60,0:31:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,bottom of the suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.20,0:31:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The partner's dinner was
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.36,0:31:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,scheduled for that same night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.30,0:31:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Neve came up in the late
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.57,0:31:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon with a dress hanging
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.15,0:31:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,from a velvet hanger.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.84,0:31:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep wine, straight neckline,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.74,0:31:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,sleeves to the elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.60,0:31:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The fabric had a specific weight
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.18,0:31:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to the touch,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.24,0:31:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that weight of something chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.63,0:31:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,with attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.88,0:31:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina looked at her without
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.00,0:31:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.18,0:31:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,From the master said Neve and
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.80,0:31:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,set the hanger on the chair
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.31,0:31:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,against the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.26,0:31:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he asked me to leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.30,0:31:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He said the miss isn't obliged
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.98,0:31:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.94,0:31:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina laughed without joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.16,0:31:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I don't wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.64,0:31:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't ask why, said Neve,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.80,0:31:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with a half smile that didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.16,0:32:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,quite complete itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.60,0:32:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But he'll notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.82,0:32:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.96,0:32:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She wore the dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.38,0:32:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She couldn't decide whether it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.79,0:32:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,was surrender or courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.30,0:32:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and she chose not to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.38,0:32:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The mansion's dining room had 18
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.97,0:32:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,places,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.88,0:32:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and a table that was a vanished
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.44,0:32:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,skating rink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.54,0:32:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There were six partners, three
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.99,0:32:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,wives,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.28,0:32:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas Ashford at one end in the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.05,0:32:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,same gray suit as always,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.86,0:32:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and the face of someone who has
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.39,0:32:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,already seen far too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.96,0:32:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,without being surprised by
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.07,0:32:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.04,0:32:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and you door a quint at the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.31,0:32:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,other end,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.28,0:32:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,seated as though the seat had
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.59,0:32:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,been built around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.98,0:32:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina entered beside Jego.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.86,0:32:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She was introduced by him in a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.41,0:32:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence that left no gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.32,0:32:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina Pike, she's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.40,0:32:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a description.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.92,0:32:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.24,0:32:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The dinner advanced through
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.52,0:32:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,courses she barely tasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.34,0:32:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There was talk of an acquisition
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.71,0:32:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,up north,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.10,0:32:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of a land auction near the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.89,0:32:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,river,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.66,0:32:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of a niece's wedding in
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.78,0:32:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Charleston.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.04,0:32:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina answered when addressed
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.49,0:32:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and listened,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.42,0:32:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,when not addressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.68,0:32:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The wine was too good to be
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.10,0:32:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,wasted on anxiety,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.60,0:32:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so she drank slowly and kept her
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.22,0:32:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,spine straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.52,0:33:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At some point between the second
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.20,0:33:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,course and the third,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.60,0:33:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Jego's hand found hers on top of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.37,0:33:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the white table cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.90,0:33:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't hold it halfway or
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.19,0:33:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,hide it under the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.74,0:33:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He left his hand resting on top
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.35,0:33:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of her hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.32,0:33:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in full view of everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.56,0:33:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and went on talking to the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.04,0:33:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,partner to his left,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.60,0:33:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the hand was some object
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.04,0:33:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd found along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.52,0:33:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and decided to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.04,0:33:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas noticed first.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.92,0:33:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina saw the small flicker in
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.30,0:33:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the lawyer's eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.50,0:33:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,almost invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.90,0:33:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,followed by a throat clearing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.25,0:33:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that made way for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.98,0:33:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodora noticed next.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.78,0:33:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The matriarch didn't take her
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.01,0:33:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes off her plate,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.20,0:33:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but her fork paused half a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.58,0:33:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,second in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.94,0:33:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and resumed moving with a care
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.52,0:33:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina had learned to interpret
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.16,0:33:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,as reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.34,0:33:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodora read people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.52,0:33:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.60,0:33:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,without appearing to be doing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.01,0:33:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.50,0:33:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After coffee the partner's rose
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.04,0:33:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for cigars,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.04,0:33:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and the wives went off to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.30,0:33:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,another parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.76,0:33:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina went up alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.22,0:33:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In the corridor she crossed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.56,0:33:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,paths with Silas,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.92,0:33:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,who carried a folder under his
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.11,0:33:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,arm and a look she couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.18,0:33:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,decipher,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.20,0:33:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the kind of look that holds more
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.59,0:34:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,than one interpretation,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.24,0:34:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and gives away none.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.22,0:34:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.20,0:34:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.06,0:34:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Mr. Ashford.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.20,0:34:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed to want to say
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.25,0:34:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.28,0:34:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He weighed the moment, decided
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.74,0:34:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,against it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.28,0:34:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and went on down the corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.78,0:34:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,with the firm stride of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.39,0:34:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with a set destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.22,0:34:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the guest room, Rowina shut
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.75,0:34:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the door and leaned against it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.28,0:34:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.42,0:34:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The wood was cold against her
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.70,0:34:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,back through the fabric of the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.02,0:34:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.72,0:34:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought about tearing up the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.13,0:34:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,notes,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.78,0:34:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,she thought about calling Hollis
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.37,0:34:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and telling him the story didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.96,0:34:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.60,0:34:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought about telling Jago
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.89,0:34:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.06,0:34:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with the wine still in her body
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.41,0:34:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and the courage of exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.20,0:34:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought about doing none of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.49,0:34:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the three things,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.72,0:34:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and leaving it all for the train
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.19,0:34:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.42,0:34:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to the bathroom, took
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.18,0:34:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,off her makeup with cold water
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.94,0:34:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and cotton,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.02,0:34:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,put on a simple linen nightgown
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.59,0:34:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,lay down on top of the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.71,0:34:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,bedspread,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.76,0:34:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and stared at the white-washed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.41,0:34:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,ceiling as the house grew quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.84,0:34:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,room by room.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.54,0:34:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She fell asleep without
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.00,0:34:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.98,0:34:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She was woken by the sound of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.28,0:34:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.12,0:34:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.36,0:35:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The door opened slowly, letting
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.80,0:35:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in a thin band of light from the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.28,0:35:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.20,0:35:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rowina saw against that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.73,0:35:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,light, the silhouette of Jago
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.38,0:35:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,quint.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.26,0:35:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't turn on the room's
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.53,0:35:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.76,0:35:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He walked to the middle of the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.30,0:35:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,room and stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.72,0:35:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and only then did she notice
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.95,0:35:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what was in his hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.44,0:35:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the file, brown, no label, no
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.21,0:35:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,rubber band now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.18,0:35:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowina sat up in the bed in a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.70,0:35:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,single motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.94,0:35:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The air left her chest in an
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.56,0:35:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,exhalation that made no sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.72,0:35:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.40,0:35:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas, he said, without raising
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.91,0:35:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,his voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.82,0:35:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he saw Odette prowling this
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.06,0:35:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.30,0:35:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought it best I checked
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.63,0:35:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,before she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.76,0:35:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice was low.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.22,0:35:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.00,0:35:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was empty of anything she
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.66,0:35:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,could use to hold on to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.46,0:35:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago looked at the file he was
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.98,0:35:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,carrying,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.02,0:35:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,leafed through a page she
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.14,0:35:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized without needing to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.44,0:35:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,look closely,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.56,0:35:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and put the page back in its
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.96,0:35:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,place,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.58,0:35:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with a care that seemed in that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.03,0:35:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.82,0:35:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the cruelest thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.10,0:35:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ballons sheets, he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.98,0:35:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,copies of old contracts, a list
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of names with notes beside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.14,0:35:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I recognized at least three of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.51,0:35:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the names.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.32,0:36:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He lifted his eyes to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.90,0:36:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.96,0:36:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't, Rowina answered,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.64,0:36:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because denying it would have
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.92,0:36:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,been a worse insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.34,0:36:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He nodded slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.78,0:36:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.86,0:36:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A single precise nod that didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.13,0:36:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,judge,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.06,0:36:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore weighed more than
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.38,0:36:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,any judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.54,0:36:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.08,0:36:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here for this, she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.28,0:36:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't know I would stop
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.72,0:36:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,coming here for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.78,0:36:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did stop weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.04,0:36:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't opened that file once
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.92,0:36:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,since.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.56,0:36:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it doesn't matter, he cut
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.16,0:36:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.68,0:36:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and even cutting in he kept his
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.34,0:36:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,usual low tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.14,0:36:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You opened it yesterday, I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.10,0:36:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.02,0:36:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were closing a
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.05,0:36:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.20,0:36:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence settled between
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.52,0:36:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,them,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.92,0:36:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with a specificity, Rowina
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.41,0:36:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't fill,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.40,0:36:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and he didn't try to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.00,0:36:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jego, thank you for coming to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.66,0:36:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Savannah,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.52,0:36:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,he said, and that was the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.56,0:36:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence that went through her
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.81,0:36:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,from side to side.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.00,0:36:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.58,0:36:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The interview is paid for, if
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.22,0:36:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you still want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.46,0:36:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I only asked that you leave
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.67,0:36:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow morning before my
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.83,0:36:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,mother comes down for coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.58,0:36:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She opened her mouth, closed it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.29,0:37:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,opened it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.14,0:37:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this like this, like
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.60,0:37:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.52,0:37:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Without yelling at me, he
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.84,0:37:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,considered the sentence,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.56,0:37:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,he took too long to answer the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.22,0:37:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of delay that is an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.93,0:37:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.88,0:37:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I yell you'll be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.03,0:37:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,think I'm still angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.50,0:37:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice found a note she had
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.02,0:37:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,never heard in him,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.14,0:37:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,too low to have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.96,0:37:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.36,0:37:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to leave knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.68,0:37:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly what stayed behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.54,0:37:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worse than yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.18,0:37:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worse than anything she
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.66,0:37:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,could have predicted that week
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.13,0:37:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or in any week before it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.36,0:37:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Jego set the file on the dresser
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.17,0:37:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,near the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.26,0:37:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with a precision that seemed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.69,0:37:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,calculated to make no noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.62,0:37:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't return it to her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.50,0:37:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't take it with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.04,0:37:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He left it there, in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.74,0:37:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.68,0:37:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,like an exposed piece of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.88,0:37:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,evidence, neither of them needed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.48,0:37:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to examine any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.78,0:37:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he turned toward the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.54,0:37:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.60,0:37:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The door closed behind him with
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.16,0:37:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the most polite noise a door has
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.78,0:37:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,ever produced in the entire
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.14,0:37:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.82,0:37:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhoina remained sitting on the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.21,0:37:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.40,0:37:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands opened on the bed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.15,0:37:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.94,0:37:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Her heart beating in a rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.36,0:37:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,she didn't recognize as her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.38,0:38:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside in the corridor, his
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.10,0:38:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps moved away slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.36,0:38:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No hurry, no hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.70,0:38:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And at some point between her
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.17,0:38:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,room and his room,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.50,0:38:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they stopped for a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.75,0:38:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,before continuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.26,0:38:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.54,0:38:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.30,0:38:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept looking at the file on
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.76,0:38:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,top of the dresser,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.94,0:38:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone staring at an
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.30,0:38:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,animal that had followed her
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.77,0:38:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,from too far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.00,0:38:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to now pretend it was a
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.09,0:38:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.52,0:38:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside the window, the garden
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.61,0:38:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Quint Mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.84,0:38:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,breathed the humid night, the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.50,0:38:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,smell of earth and jasmine
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.99,0:38:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,rising with the breeze off the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.72,0:38:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,river.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.46,0:38:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere near the water, a real
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.33,0:38:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,owl called out once.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.08,0:38:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhoina thought of the glass owl
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.59,0:38:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,set with red stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.96,0:38:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,tucked in a dark velvet box at
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.45,0:38:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the bottom of her bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.98,0:38:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and felt that this was the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.28,0:38:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,memory that would hurt most on
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.77,0:38:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the train the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.48,0:38:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But chapter 5 killing the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.66,0:38:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain back left before 8, and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.57,0:38:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhoina sat by the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.68,0:38:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because the aisle required
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.91,0:38:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at people head on,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.48,0:38:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and people that morning would
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.96,0:39:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,have seen what she hadn't yet
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.43,0:39:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,seen in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.90,0:39:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She rested her forehead against
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.45,0:39:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the cold glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.66,0:39:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and stayed that way for a length
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.08,0:39:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of time she couldn't measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.94,0:39:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Savannah fell behind in pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.74,0:39:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a roof, a tower, a line of trees
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.59,0:39:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,bent by the river wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.42,0:39:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and none of it hurt with the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.51,0:39:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,noise she had expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.40,0:39:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurt low. It hurt the way
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.87,0:39:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago had said,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.28,0:39:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you in the small hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.84,0:39:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,when she was expecting a shout,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.88,0:39:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,anything with enough volume for
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.22,0:39:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,her to push back against,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.82,0:39:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the file was still on top of the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.34,0:39:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,guest room dresser.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.52,0:39:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She hadn't even asked for it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.20,0:39:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,back, leaving it there felt
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.82,0:39:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.36,0:39:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sense that justice is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.63,0:39:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what's left over when everything
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.09,0:39:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,else surrenders.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.28,0:39:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't cry on the train. She
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.09,0:39:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,counted roof panels of cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.30,0:39:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,counted poles, counted the times
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.97,0:39:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the conductor passed down the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.49,0:39:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,aisle dragging a coffee cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.40,0:39:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of the machine coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.13,0:39:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,was cheap, and watery.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.94,0:39:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like what Jago had
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.37,0:39:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,learned to make, and that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.75,0:39:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,idiotic detail was what came
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.30,0:39:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,closest to breaking her. She
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.94,0:39:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,reached the grey city just
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.46,0:39:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,before noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.52,0:39:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The station smelled of lubricant
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.24,0:40:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and cheap bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.60,0:40:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena carried her suitcase like
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.99,0:40:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,someone carrying a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.64,0:40:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She cried in the newsroom
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.85,0:40:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.62,0:40:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dry cry of two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.88,0:40:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Curled up in a stall with her
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.23,0:40:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,hand over her mouth because
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.49,0:40:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlo Trent was on the other
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.79,0:40:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,side of the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.58,0:40:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tapping the tip of her shoe and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.42,0:40:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,speaking loudly to cover for
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.08,0:40:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.56,0:40:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out of their pike. If you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.20,0:40:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,stay in there any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.92,0:40:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis is going to knock on the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.17,0:40:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,door and then I'm going to have
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.42,0:40:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to bite him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.18,0:40:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena laughed in the middle of
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.68,0:40:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the cry without meaning to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.26,0:40:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an ugly sound but it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.78,0:40:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.64,0:40:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She came out with her face
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.05,0:40:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,washed. Marlo looked at her for
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.73,0:40:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole second,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.04,0:40:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,without sarcasm for the first
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.55,0:40:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,time in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.78,0:40:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something different in
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.91,0:40:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,her friend's expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.34,0:40:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The shoulders quieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.32,0:40:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she stood still without
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.07,0:40:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,her phone in her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.80,0:40:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay? No. Rowena answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.00,0:40:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will be. Marlo squeezed
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.79,0:40:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,her shoulder and her hand stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.77,0:40:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there too long for a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.78,0:40:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was how Rowena understood
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.17,0:40:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,her friend had guessed
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.18,0:40:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,everything before asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.94,0:40:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The newsroom had that midday
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.39,0:40:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.20,0:41:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Keys, phones ringing two desks
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.05,0:41:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,over.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.68,0:41:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone shouting a page number
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.21,0:41:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,down the hall as if the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.69,0:41:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,building needed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.92,0:41:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis Vaughan lifted his eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.57,0:41:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,over his glasses the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.06,0:41:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena passed down the central
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.71,0:41:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.50,0:41:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't smile. He didn't ask
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.12,0:41:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,how the trip had gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.70,0:41:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He simply pointed with his pen
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.16,0:41:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to the door of his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.78,0:41:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A short, habitual gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.06,0:41:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind that allows no
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.24,0:41:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.54,0:41:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She went in. She shut the door
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.33,0:41:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,behind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.24,0:41:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That office smelled of aged
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.61,0:41:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,paper and coffee no one had the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.18,0:41:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,courage to throw out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.60,0:41:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a plant in the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.02,0:41:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,corner that had been dying for
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.54,0:41:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,at least two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.56,0:41:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's leaves drooping over the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.35,0:41:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,edge of the pot without anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.21,0:41:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,having noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.66,0:41:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis sat down his pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.36,0:41:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Headline, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.76,0:41:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,End of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.90,0:41:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not going to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.86,0:41:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,headline.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.80,0:41:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis blinked once.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.38,0:41:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He leaned back in his chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.98,0:41:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.24,0:41:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not going to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.57,0:41:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,headline Rowena repeated and her
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.27,0:41:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,voice came out firm
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.28,0:41:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of them she expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.68,0:41:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to deliver what
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.15,0:41:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.04,0:41:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today, not next week, not
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.12,0:41:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.96,0:42:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You went there with a mission
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.46,0:42:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.72,0:42:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I did, and I came back without
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.61,0:42:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.16,0:42:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis looked at the desk for a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.47,0:42:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.24,0:42:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When he raised his eyes, there
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.75,0:42:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,was less anger than she'd
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.01,0:42:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.06,0:42:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And more a kind of old
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.19,0:42:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,disappointment, the kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.58,0:42:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,disappointment bosses carry from
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.22,0:42:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,other
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.48,0:42:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,bosses before them, piled up
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.32,0:42:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,over years in rooms exactly like
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.43,0:42:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.20,0:42:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what this means.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.86,0:42:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.84,0:42:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena set a folded paper on the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.60,0:42:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.24,0:42:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm handing this over before you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.86,0:42:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.04,0:42:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis picked up the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.44,0:42:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.66,0:42:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.52,0:42:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.32,0:42:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question came almost
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.81,0:42:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,gentle, which frightened her
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.31,0:42:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,more than an insult would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.30,0:42:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena was silent for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.06,0:42:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought of a pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.13,0:42:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,professional answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.56,0:42:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind that looks good in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.68,0:42:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,retrospect.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.58,0:42:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.62,0:42:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the story stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.11,0:42:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,existing, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.60,0:42:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped being a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.28,0:42:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know how to write
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.60,0:42:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,about someone who became a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.78,0:42:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,person.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.44,0:42:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis looked at her for a long
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.94,0:42:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,time, with the expression of
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.29,0:42:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,someone re-reading an equation
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.75,0:42:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.94,0:42:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't add up, then he nodded
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.86,0:42:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,once, almost imperceptibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.08,0:43:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out before I change my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.95,0:43:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.84,0:43:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And Pike, she stopped at the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.57,0:43:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,door.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.34,0:43:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.40,0:43:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena swallowed before
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.43,0:43:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.48,0:43:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I still am.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.60,0:43:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just not for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.96,0:43:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She shut the door carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.72,0:43:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollis was leaning against the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.28,0:43:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor wall, waiting with two
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.89,0:43:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,cups of machine coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.56,0:43:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And she pushed one of the cups
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.14,0:43:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,into Rowena's hand without
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.52,0:43:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,ceremony, like someone handing
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.10,0:43:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,over a
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.42,0:43:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,survival item.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.64,0:43:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.72,0:43:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.22,0:43:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.74,0:43:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.68,0:43:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlo Blue on the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.46,0:43:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the club of the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.67,0:43:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,dignified unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.58,0:43:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.66,0:43:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a short, broken laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.55,0:43:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.22,0:43:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They went down the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.19,0:43:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.78,0:43:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,On the sidewalk, the city was
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.44,0:43:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,grey the way it had always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.70,0:43:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rowena looked at the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.86,0:43:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,buildings without any of the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.22,0:43:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,glow that Savannah painted on to
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.77,0:43:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,even a
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.06,0:43:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,cloudy morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.36,0:43:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Something was missing from that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.18,0:43:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.86,0:43:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of Magnolia was
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.31,0:43:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.78,0:43:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The way the Savannah river
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.26,0:43:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared between two streets
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.85,0:43:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,when no one expected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.42,0:44:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A strip of lead-coloured water
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.13,0:44:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that somehow made everything
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.72,0:44:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,lighter was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.32,0:44:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,E was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.94,0:44:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going back, Marlo said,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.75,0:44:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.26,0:44:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.24,0:44:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he take you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.56,0:44:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.52,0:44:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He will.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.34,0:44:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlo insisted looking off into
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.74,0:44:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.96,0:44:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who sends for you three
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.71,0:44:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks in a row doesn't close a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.52,0:44:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,door for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.76,0:44:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He locks it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.84,0:44:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.46,0:44:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena looked at her friend, and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.41,0:44:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,for an instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.84,0:44:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the world stopped spinning so
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.29,0:44:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.14,0:44:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Marlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.96,0:44:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.66,0:44:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.54,0:44:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here before I cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.33,0:44:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.12,0:44:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.80,0:44:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena took the night train and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.35,0:44:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,slept enough not to look
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.56,0:44:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,devastated on arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.08,0:44:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The car smelled of old fabric
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.62,0:44:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and rain, and she kept her face
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.27,0:44:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,turned to the dark window
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.60,0:44:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,for much of the trip, watching
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.18,0:44:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,her own reflection without being
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.87,0:44:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,able to look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.32,0:44:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,On Sunday morning, Savannah
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.68,0:44:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,received the train with the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.23,0:44:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,coming in from the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.44,0:44:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And the whole station smelled of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.29,0:44:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,bakery and river breeze,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.24,0:44:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,she took a taxi without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.75,0:44:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.58,0:44:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She went in through the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.36,0:45:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She rang the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.80,0:45:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.70,0:45:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes widened for half a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.19,0:45:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,second, before returning to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.69,0:45:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,normal trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.10,0:45:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Pike, I need to talk to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.85,0:45:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.30,0:45:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in his office with guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.26,0:45:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.32,0:45:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling hesitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.78,0:45:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he stepped aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.30,0:45:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss is quint arrived in our
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.72,0:45:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.16,0:45:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He said quietly, almost a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.68,0:45:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.74,0:45:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And Miss Martian came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.40,0:45:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena nodded.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.06,0:45:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Druid deep breath once and
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.28,0:45:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,walked down the marble corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.36,0:45:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone walking to a trial
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.76,0:45:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,she herself had scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.54,0:45:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The corridor was silent except
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.87,0:45:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,for her own footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.48,0:45:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And their echo on the old tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.97,0:45:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,sounded too firm for the way she
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.51,0:45:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was feeling inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.00,0:45:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jay goes office was in the west
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.61,0:45:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,wing of the mansion, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.06,0:45:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,door was a jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.28,0:45:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She heard before she saw, the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.34,0:45:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,voice of Odette Martian, sweet,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.54,0:45:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,too loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.66,0:45:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that voice of someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.95,0:45:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,pretends to console and measures
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.60,0:45:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the effect in a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.78,0:45:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A necessary evil you'dora.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.64,0:45:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, better to find out now
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.50,0:45:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,than, Rowena opened the door
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.30,0:45:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,before Odette finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.30,0:45:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire office went still.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.18,0:46:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Jay goes to behind the desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.81,0:46:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,dark jacket hands resting on the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.67,0:46:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,top.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.26,0:46:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'dora seated in the green
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.50,0:46:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,velvet armchair near the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.44,0:46:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,back straight as ever, as if her
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.15,0:46:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,posture were the last line of
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.69,0:46:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.80,0:46:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas leaning against the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.12,0:46:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,bookcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.04,0:46:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Neutral expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.50,0:46:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyes that recognized Rowena
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.81,0:46:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,before the rest of his body did.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.36,0:46:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Odette on the sofa, glass in
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.29,0:46:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,hand, a smile dressing her mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.50,0:46:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,until it froze when she saw
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.36,0:46:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,who had come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.68,0:46:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaygo didn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.06,0:46:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Only his jaw tensed once.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.20,0:46:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena said Silas almost
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.72,0:46:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically, trying to smooth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.68,0:46:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,things over.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.82,0:46:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay, Rowena asked, without
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.38,0:46:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,taking her eyes off Jaygo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.44,0:46:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.40,0:46:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.24,0:46:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Odette opened her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.84,0:46:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena gave her no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.72,0:46:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to tell the truth, she
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.56,0:46:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,said.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.24,0:46:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.90,0:46:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to apologise first
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.76,0:46:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because an apology before the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.44,0:46:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,truth is an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.18,0:46:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Odora raised an eyebrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.80,0:46:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.96,0:46:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena breathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.26,0:46:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Her voice came out firm, even
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.94,0:46:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,though her hands trembled inside
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.80,0:46:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,her jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.96,0:47:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to Savannah with two
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.30,0:47:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.38,0:47:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The interview was one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.78,0:47:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The other was to come back with
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.18,0:47:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,material that would destroy the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.57,0:47:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Quint family.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.68,0:47:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My editor wanted a scandal
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.15,0:47:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,story, and I accepted because I
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.89,0:47:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,needed the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.20,0:47:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I accepted believing I could
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.57,0:47:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,separate the work from the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.85,0:47:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,charade.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.24,0:47:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She paused.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.86,0:47:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.86,0:47:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Odette let out a low incredulous
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.80,0:47:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.50,0:47:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No one joined her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.88,0:47:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the file, Rowena
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.38,0:47:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,continued, and her voice didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.17,0:47:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.04,0:47:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know I brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.76,0:47:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.98,0:47:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was red.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.14,0:47:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was returned in the small
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.64,0:47:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,hours of yesterday morning with
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.09,0:47:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.60,0:47:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that hurt more than any shout
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.21,0:47:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.08,0:47:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked at Jaygo.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.42,0:47:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.60,0:47:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.96,0:47:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His face was that of a man
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.44,0:47:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,counting every word before
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.92,0:47:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,deciding what to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.62,0:47:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have gone back to the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.47,0:47:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,newsroom, written what my editor
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.51,0:47:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted, saved my career.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.54,0:47:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A voice rose half a tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.48,0:47:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.68,0:47:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed the story this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.56,0:47:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I resigned before he could fire
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.29,0:47:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.76,0:47:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no story anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.34,0:48:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no file anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.00,0:48:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left in that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.27,0:48:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,guest room that's of use to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.50,0:48:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.22,0:48:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She took a step forward just
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.81,0:48:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.34,0:48:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't come here for
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.42,0:48:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.52,0:48:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I came because if I didn't say
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.88,0:48:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this in front of everyone who
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.20,0:48:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,watched the lie happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.24,0:48:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth would remain a private
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.23,0:48:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,thing and the lie was public.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.50,0:48:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.02,0:48:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Total silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.52,0:48:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Udora blinked once.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.10,0:48:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.98,0:48:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone recalculating
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.22,0:48:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,something she'd thought was
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.50,0:48:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.40,0:48:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,O'Dette looked at her glasses if
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.99,0:48:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it had betrayed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.14,0:48:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.58,0:48:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena said.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.56,0:48:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And her voice lowered again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.30,0:48:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.54,0:48:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he stopped being a
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.00,0:48:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,story.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.84,0:48:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't write about a man who
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.27,0:48:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,learned my coffee by heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.86,0:48:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.44,0:48:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The hands were still trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.64,0:48:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She let them tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.16,0:48:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,O'Dette rose first.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.30,0:48:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Her glass coming down hard on
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.82,0:48:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the side tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.96,0:48:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What a spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.34,0:48:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She said.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.34,0:48:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeking Jago's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.92,0:48:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to believe this
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.18,0:48:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.98,0:48:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago didn't answer O'Dette.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.86,0:48:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at Rowena for a length
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.42,0:48:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of time no one there could
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.69,0:48:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,count.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.40,0:49:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he pulled back his chair
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.07,0:49:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,unhurried and stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.74,0:49:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,J.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.88,0:49:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 6 His laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.29,0:49:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Go cross the office in a single
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.99,0:49:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,stride.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.37,0:49:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't seem like a stride it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.00,0:49:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,seemed like decision walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.13,0:49:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena didn't step back but she
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.65,0:49:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,held her breath in the middle of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.23,0:49:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,her chest
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.67,0:49:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,as if her body had forgotten how
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.62,0:49:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.33,0:49:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped half a meter from
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.84,0:49:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.25,0:49:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.57,0:49:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He just stood there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.07,0:49:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes fixed on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.79,0:49:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was something in that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.23,0:49:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,gaze Rowena couldn't name.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.85,0:49:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither anger nor relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.75,0:49:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that made her hold her
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.12,0:49:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,own breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.01,0:49:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,O'Dette.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.73,0:49:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He said without looking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.41,0:49:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.87,0:49:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence in the room had
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.12,0:49:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.45,0:49:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of silence that makes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.90,0:49:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,people hold their breath without
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.45,0:49:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,realizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.69,0:49:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.63,0:49:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, his voice came out low.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.19,0:49:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Curtis.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.97,0:49:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he spoke to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.81,0:49:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And even so, no one in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.57,0:49:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,had any doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.85,0:49:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,O'Dette picked up her bag with
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.17,0:49:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,rigid movements her fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.35,0:49:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,gripping the leather.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.67,0:49:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't look at you, Dora.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.29,0:49:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The door slammed behind her with
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.07,0:49:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the thin noise of high heels
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.63,0:50:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that had lost their audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.75,0:50:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago breathed once.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.35,0:50:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he looked at Rowena as if
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.94,0:50:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,he were checking a calculation
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.53,0:50:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that had taken
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.27,0:50:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,far too long to add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.13,0:50:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to hear this," he
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.84,0:50:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,said.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.43,0:50:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Loud enough for siless and you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.09,0:50:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dora to hear every word.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.85,0:50:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And loud enough to carry through
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.31,0:50:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the open door and reach the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.54,0:50:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.51,0:50:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where half a dozen of you Dora's
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.02,0:50:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,guests pretended not to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.97,0:50:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She stays.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.23,0:50:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,With me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.17,0:50:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow, all of Savannah
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.81,0:50:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,will hear it from my mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.29,0:50:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,before hearing it from anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.93,0:50:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.49,0:50:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He paused for an instant, as if
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.10,0:50:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the sentence carried weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.01,0:50:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done letting fear choose for
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.51,0:50:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.05,0:50:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He raised his hand slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.39,0:50:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He touched the tips of his
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.81,0:50:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,fingers to her chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.31,0:50:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The touch has light as a
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.43,0:50:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,question.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.57,0:50:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.49,0:50:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena felt her eyes sting.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.41,0:50:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.79,0:50:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.85,0:50:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas let out the air he'd been
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.20,0:50:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.09,0:50:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Udora didn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.57,0:50:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But something in the line of her
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.90,0:50:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders gave way a millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.75,0:50:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the matriarch who broke
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.32,0:50:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the silence at last,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.79,0:50:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,with that voice that never
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.02,0:50:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,missed its tone even on hard
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.35,0:50:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,days.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.09,0:51:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of here, she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.19,0:51:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,addressing neither of them in
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.64,0:51:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.77,0:51:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you I need to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.15,0:51:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena and Jago left together.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.89,0:51:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas closed the door with the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.26,0:51:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,care of someone who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.41,0:51:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that a well-closed door is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.07,0:51:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes worth an entire
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.66,0:51:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.75,0:51:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In the corridor Jago held
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.17,0:51:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.41,0:51:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.53,0:51:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't kiss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.71,0:51:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.87,0:51:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He just held it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.55,0:51:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,His fingers laced through hers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.33,0:51:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with a quiet firmness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.15,0:51:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike anything she'd known in
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.60,0:51:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,him until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.71,0:51:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He let her out onto the back
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.08,0:51:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,porch.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.87,0:51:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The one facing the Savannah
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.20,0:51:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,River.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.49,0:51:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The late afternoon sun fell gold
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.63,0:51:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and on the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.25,0:51:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,tinting the surface copper and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.87,0:51:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,amber,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.57,0:51:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the smell of the garden came
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.38,0:51:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,heavy with magnolia wet from the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.19,0:51:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.41,0:51:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in the middle of the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.10,0:51:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,garden, an insect sang the same
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.84,0:51:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,repeated note,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.97,0:51:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhythmic in No Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.97,0:51:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed the story, said Jago,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.96,0:51:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.69,0:51:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.31,0:51:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.21,0:51:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.87,0:51:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.63,0:51:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He turned his head slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.71,0:52:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and his profile against the late
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.48,0:52:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon light had a hardness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.13,0:52:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena couldn't read in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.25,0:52:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She could only read the part
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.37,0:52:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.41,0:52:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to help you find
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.67,0:52:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,another one, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.09,0:52:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.35,0:52:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one I choose for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.29,0:52:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena laughed softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.81,0:52:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The laugh came out choked.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.35,0:52:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A little crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.45,0:52:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The way laughs happen when the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.87,0:52:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,body doesn't quite know yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.43,0:52:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's crying or smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.65,0:52:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You said choose and for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.97,0:52:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In the same sentence, quint.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.75,0:52:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.67,0:52:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He closed his eyes for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.09,0:52:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When he opened them, his
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.46,0:52:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders had dropped half a
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.07,0:52:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,finger,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.97,0:52:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and his mouth gave way in a near
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.80,0:52:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,smile Rowena had never seen
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.35,0:52:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.97,0:52:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.97,0:52:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was there behind them that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.91,0:52:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the porch door opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.95,0:52:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora came out without
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.21,0:52:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,announcing herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.53,0:52:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't look at Jago first.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.31,0:52:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked at Rowena, and there
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.04,0:52:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,was in that gaze and a
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.27,0:52:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,preysal different from the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.70,0:52:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier ones without the usual
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.35,0:52:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.21,0:52:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The matriarch crossed the stone
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.95,0:52:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.75,0:52:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and stopped in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.99,0:52:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Up close in the low rosy light
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.66,0:52:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of that afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.37,0:53:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora seemed smaller than on
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.53,0:53:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the night of the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.01,0:53:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Smaller and older and less
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.85,0:53:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,sharp,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.61,0:53:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as if she'd left her armor
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.86,0:53:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,hanging on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.47,0:53:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena waited for the blow that
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.10,0:53:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.17,0:53:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora extended her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.97,0:53:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She touched Rowena's arm
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.22,0:53:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.19,0:53:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A thumb sliding once over the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.50,0:53:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,sleeve of the jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.07,0:53:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A gesture so restrained it could
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.59,0:53:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,have gone unnoticed, but it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.88,0:53:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.49,0:53:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she turned her head and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.92,0:53:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,looked into the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.23,0:53:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The wide door was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.45,0:53:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And from there you could see the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.14,0:53:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,empty chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.13,0:53:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that had always been
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.32,0:53:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,near the window of the main
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.46,0:53:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.99,0:53:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Its back turned slightly to the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.64,0:53:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,side,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.25,0:53:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as if someone had just stood up
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.64,0:53:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and would come back at any
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.82,0:53:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.65,0:53:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora kept looking long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.06,0:53:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,for the moment to grow heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.85,0:53:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You have his laugh, she
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.09,0:53:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,murmured.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.11,0:53:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena didn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.79,0:53:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She felt her heart skipped a
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.07,0:53:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,whole beat,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.91,0:53:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but she didn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.71,0:53:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora didn't explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.19,0:53:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She just squeezed her arm once
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.70,0:53:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,very lightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.83,0:53:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and went back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.85,0:53:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The door closed behind her
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.40,0:53:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,without a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.85,0:53:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As if the house were protecting
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.53,0:53:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that secret too.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.75,0:53:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowena looked at Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.39,0:54:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His jaw was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.73,0:54:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,His gaze fixed on some point of
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.42,0:54:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the river
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.91,0:54:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that no longer belonged to that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.50,0:54:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.71,0:54:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.73,0:54:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, he said quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.69,0:54:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, she didn't insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.91,0:54:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She stored the question in the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.26,0:54:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,same place where she stored all
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.65,0:54:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the details
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.15,0:54:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that didn't yet have a frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.25,0:54:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept storing, because that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.84,0:54:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,was what she knew how to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.33,0:54:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And because not every detail
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.81,0:54:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,asked to be opened on the same
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.39,0:54:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,day it appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.73,0:54:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yudora back inside at the end of
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.32,0:54:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.59,0:54:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When the river was already dark
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.04,0:54:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.73,0:54:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mansions lights were
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.04,0:54:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning to come on one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.85,0:54:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the house were breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.59,0:54:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They ate little.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.77,0:54:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No one spoke much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.31,0:54:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas passed down the corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.84,0:54:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,once,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.53,0:54:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,nodded agreeding, and vanished
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.06,0:54:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,off towards the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.79,0:54:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nive brought T without asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.43,0:54:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and disappeared before anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.02,0:54:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,could thank her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.11,0:54:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it was Jago who extended
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.68,0:54:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.17,0:54:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowen were accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.95,0:54:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They went up the main staircase
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.50,0:54:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,together.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.37,0:54:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Her footsteps echoed on the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.80,0:54:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,marble.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.67,0:54:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,His almost didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.67,0:54:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He always stepped as if he
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.82,0:55:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't want to take up more
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.02,0:55:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,space than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.57,0:55:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Half way up the stairs he
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.54,0:55:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.39,0:55:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He turned her slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.83,0:55:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand displayed against the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.11,0:55:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,nape of her neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.19,0:55:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and pressed his forehead to hers
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.60,0:55:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,for a length of time that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.70,0:55:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,belonged to no clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.93,0:55:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.16,0:55:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.79,0:55:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, too low to be anything
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.50,0:55:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.71,0:55:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No one does.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.93,0:55:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.39,0:55:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a short laugh almost
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.10,0:55:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,startled.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.11,0:55:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of laugh that escapes
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.57,0:55:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,before a person decides to let
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.03,0:55:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.73,0:55:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rowen restored that laugh too.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.35,0:55:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She stored it the same way she
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.67,0:55:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,stored everything that mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.47,0:55:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Without noting it down, without
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.33,0:55:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,recording it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.33,0:55:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just letting it settle deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.61,0:55:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.85,0:55:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At the top the corridor had that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.48,0:55:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,late night mansion silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.29,0:55:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that isn't the silence of
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.36,0:55:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.43,0:55:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the silence of care.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.21,0:55:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The door to his room was a jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.21,0:55:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He pushed it with the back of
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.46,0:55:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.85,0:55:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A casual gesture that contained
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.75,0:55:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.41,0:55:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.31,0:55:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He went in behind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.93,0:55:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The door closed slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.75,0:55:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.71,0:55:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.07,0:55:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Smelled of coffee and warm
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.45,0:55:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.29,0:55:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Savannah light came in from
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.60,0:56:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the side through the high
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.65,0:56:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,window,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.45,0:56:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,cut into bands by the frames,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.47,0:56:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and fell gold and over the white
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.03,0:56:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,tablecloth,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.95,0:56:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,over the cups, over the still
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.68,0:56:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,warm loaves that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.63,0:56:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,neither had left in a basket,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.27,0:56:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and disappeared before anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.64,0:56:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,could thank her.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.51,0:56:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That was how Nive did things,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.09,0:56:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,beforehand and without making
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.01,0:56:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.95,0:56:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Roena sat with her legs crossed
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.32,0:56:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in the chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.29,0:56:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the cup warming both her hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.55,0:56:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jego sat beside her, so close
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.24,0:56:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that his knee touched hers under
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.11,0:56:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.15,0:56:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.27,0:56:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He just extended his hand over
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.74,0:56:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the white tablecloth and waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.87,0:56:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Roena placed hers on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.75,0:56:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They stayed that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.11,0:56:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unhurried.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.11,0:56:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,While the heat of the coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.52,0:56:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,rose in a thread of steam
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.78,0:56:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.57,0:56:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked at the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.81,0:56:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He had made the coffee the way
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.22,0:56:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,she liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.13,0:56:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Two dashes of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.25,0:56:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,More milk than any barista would
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.22,0:56:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.07,0:56:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd made it without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.73,0:56:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She smiled into the cup and said
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.55,0:56:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.51,0:56:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,because she didn't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.05,0:56:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,From the other side of the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.01,0:56:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.69,0:56:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,through the arch doorway you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.90,0:56:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,could see the corner of the main
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.27,0:56:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.93,0:56:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And from there you could see the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.18,0:56:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,empty chair near the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.75,0:57:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Its back was still turned
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.02,0:57:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,slightly to the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.45,0:57:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,as it had been the afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.84,0:57:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,before,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.65,0:57:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as on every morning Roena had
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.22,0:57:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,spent in that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.71,0:57:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No one had moved the chair
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.97,0:57:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.21,0:57:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No one had occupied it as far as
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.94,0:57:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,she knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.43,0:57:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,On any of the times she'd been
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.38,0:57:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.07,0:57:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Alaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.01,0:57:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone you'd orah had known.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.89,0:57:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone Jago had known.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.73,0:57:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A name the house had decided to
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.43,0:57:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,stop saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.55,0:57:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,guarded with such care that even
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.15,0:57:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the silence around it had shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.39,0:57:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Roena opened her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.01,0:57:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.95,0:57:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He lifted his eyes from the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.11,0:57:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.89,0:57:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.11,0:57:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.87,0:57:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and her voice came out soft,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.56,0:57:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.77,0:57:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so as not to break that morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.55,0:57:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.21,0:57:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,About a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.99,0:57:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jago's hand overhears tightened
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.25,0:57:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.27,0:57:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.35,0:57:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A small involuntary squeeze the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.09,0:57:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,kind that happens before a
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.54,0:57:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,person decides to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.11,0:57:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.79,0:57:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.07,0:57:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because he interrupted her
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.42,0:57:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,with any word.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.41,0:57:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the silence that did the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.84,0:57:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,work.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.45,0:57:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole round silence that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.69,0:57:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,filled the table and the coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.69,0:58:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and the savanna light falling
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.13,0:58:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,between them,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.97,0:58:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the sun too were waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.27,0:58:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at the cup,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.63,0:58:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,then at her hand under his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.49,0:58:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then for a very brief instant at
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.22,0:58:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the empty chair far off
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.47,0:58:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,golden in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.85,0:58:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.17,0:58:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Roena felt then with a cold and
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.92,0:58:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,new certainty
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.65,0:58:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was an entire story
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.42,0:58:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,living inside that house,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.35,0:58:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,not in the walls or the old
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.66,0:58:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,furniture,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.75,0:58:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the people who lived in
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.05,0:58:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it and carried it without saying
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.44,0:58:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.27,0:58:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She had just knocked on the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.41,0:58:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,right door.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.31,0:58:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The door was not going to open
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.75,0:58:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.71,0:58:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She stored the question in her
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.12,0:58:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.83,0:58:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she had always stored
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.20,0:58:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what didn't yet have its time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.99,0:58:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She closed her hand around his.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.13,0:58:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside a bird sang a high note
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.05,0:58:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and flew away.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.91,0:58:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The empty chair remained empty,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.35,0:58:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,golden in the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.61,0:58:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,occupying the place it had
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.71,0:58:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,always occupied,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.95,0:58:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and she understood without
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.28,0:58:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone needing to say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.81,0:58:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that that morning of peace was
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.30,0:58:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,only the beginning of something
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.84,0:58:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,else.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.67,0:59:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Six months later, she woke up
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.54,0:59:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,every day in Jago's arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.61,0:59:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In the dream house he had built
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.12,0:59:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.09,0:59:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow kisses, whispered promises,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.15,0:59:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,his body fitted to hers as if
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.08,0:59:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the world outside didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.79,0:59:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the bodyguard started
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.12,0:59:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,following her into the more
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.45,0:59:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.79,0:59:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Until he deleted the job offer
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.38,0:59:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that had come for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.61,0:59:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,without saying a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.09,0:59:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the phone rang and a name,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.11,0:59:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a name no one in that family
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.44,0:59:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,dare to speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.65,0:59:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,may Jago go pale, hang up
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.44,0:59:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,mid-sentence,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.89,0:59:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and lie with his eyes still
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.40,0:59:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,glazed with dread.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.39,0:59:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw the raw fear there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.07,0:59:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The same fear he had been hiding
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.87,0:59:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,since the night they kissed for
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.61,0:59:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.79,0:59:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending it was only a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.91,0:59:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The old secret between them was
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.40,0:59:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.83,0:59:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an open wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.55,0:59:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Capable of explaining the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.91,0:59:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,controlling man Jago had become,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.09,0:59:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and of destroying forever the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.62,0:59:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,man she had loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.87,1:00:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she trembled alone in the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.29,1:00:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,luxurious bedroom,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.69,1:00:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,tasting the bitter flavor of
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.19,1:00:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,betrayed trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.71,1:00:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if the past he had
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.91,1:00:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,locked away with guilt
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.89,1:00:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,was greater than the love he
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.66,1:00:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,swore he felt.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.55,1:00:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if opening that door
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.34,1:00:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,made him hate her forever?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.39,1:00:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if the beautiful golden
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.92,1:00:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,cage was the only thing still
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.30,1:00:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,keeping the two of them
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.40,1:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,together?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.96,1:01:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,side.